This is a python program written to manage certain harware features for a Samsung Series9 ultrabook, specifically NP900X3D.

It started as a frontend for some scripts that were designed to do the same thing.
this is a little python frontend im writing for some scripts i also wrote

Current effort is to make it as generically applicable as I can figure it to be.

Due to fiddling with hardware settings under /sys/, it will need root priviledges.
